OL,3,CHealth unions urge Executive to
OL,4,Cimplement pay increase
OL,6,FHealth unions have urged the Executive
OL,7,Fto implement a pay recommendation that
OL,8,Fwould see workers get an above
OL,9,Finflation increase to their salary.
OL,11,FAn independent body has recommended a
OL,12,F5.5% increase for this year, with a
OL,13,Ffurther recommendation that doctors
OL,14,Fand dentists should get 6%.
OL,16,FThe recommendations by the Review Body
OL,17,Fon Doctors' and Dentists' Remuneration
OL,18,F(DDRB) are being implemented for staff
OL,19,Fin England.
