OL,3,CHealth unions urge Executive to
OL,4,Cimplement pay increase
OL,6,FIt means additional funds will filter
OL,7,Fdown to Stormont - however the health
OL,8,Fminister says he's unable to make an
OL,9,Fimmediate decision, despite being
OL,10,Fsupportive in principle of the uplift.
OL,12,F"I am supportive of the
OL,13,Frecommendations in principle," said
OL,14,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt.
OL,16,F"The severe budgetary pressures on
OL,17,Fhealth and social care in Northern
OL,18,FIreland means I am unable to make an
OL,19,Fimmediate decision on the
OL,20,Frecommendations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
