OL,6,F"This is very regrettable, but I can
OL,7,Fassure staff I will do everything in
OL,8,Fmy power to ensure they are properly
OL,9,Frewarded."
OL,11,FIn a statement, Dr Clodagh Corrigan
OL,12,Ffrom the BMA said Northern Ireland
OL,13,F"cannot continually be lagging behind".
OL,15,FShe said this would be "damaging to
OL,16,Fmorale and ultimately to patient care".
