OL,3,CHealth unions urge Executive to
OL,4,Cimplement pay increase
OL,6,FDr Corrigan said: "We note that the
OL,7,FDDRB has recommended an uplift of 6%
OL,8,Ffor all doctors with an additional
OL,9,F#1,000 non consolidated award for
OL,10,Fdoctors in training," she said.
OL,12,F"This is a step in the right direction
OL,13,Fto improve doctors pay, but there is
OL,14,Fstill work to be done to address the
OL,15,Fpay erosion doctors have faced.
OL,17,F"Only by doing that will we retain
OL,18,Fdoctors in the health service here and
OL,19,Faddress the shameful waiting lists and
OL,20,Fdelays in treatment patients face.
OL,26,@nD@SOUtD@AOU
