OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F449A1722456028
OL,3,CHealth unions urge Executive to
OL,4,Cimplement pay increase
OL,6,F"It is however deeply concerning to
OL,7,Fsee the Department of Health
OL,8,Findicating they will not be able to
OL,9,Fafford the pay uplift without cuts to
OL,10,Fservices.
OL,12,F"The government in England has said
OL,13,Fthat it accepts this recommendation
OL,14,Fand will apply it to doctors there.
OL,16,F"Therefore our own health minister now
OL,17,Fneeds to ensure that the same uplift
OL,18,Fis applied to doctors here as quickly
OL,19,Fas possible.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
