OL,3,CHealth unions urge Executive to
OL,4,Cimplement pay increase
OL,6,F"As noted by the DDRB, the uplift for
OL,7,F2023 was finally paid in June 2024,
OL,8,Fmonths later than the rest of the UK.
OL,9,FThis is totally unacceptable and needs
OL,10,Fto be rectified. We cannot continually
OL,11,Fbe lagging behind, it is damaging to
OL,12,Fmorale and ultimately to patient care."
OL,14,FDr Corrigan continued: "An improved
OL,15,Foffer has also been made today to
OL,16,Fjunior doctors in England.
OL,26,@vD@XOU
