OL,3,CHealth unions urge Executive to
OL,4,Cimplement pay increase
OL,6,F"The health minister here now needs to
OL,7,Fwork quickly to assess the impact
OL,8,Fthere will be if a substantially
OL,9,Fimproved pay offer is not now made to
OL,10,Fjunior doctors in Northern Ireland,
OL,11,Fthis is the only way to avert further
OL,12,Fand longer strike action.
OL,14,F"SAS doctors here are also moving
OL,15,Ftowards balloting for industrial
OL,16,Faction as they see their pay falling
OL,17,Ffurther behind the rest of the UK with
OL,18,Fsuccessful negotiations in other
OL,19,Fnations resulting in resolution of pay
OL,20,Fdisputes and averted industrial action.
